Table of Contents
I: Abyss difficulty added to ES/Elite Supes
II: Added fancy health bar to ES/Elite Supes
III: New Episode Quest
IV: New Sub Quest


I: Abyss difficulty added to ES/Elite Supes
REQUIRED TO ENTER: 1 Radiant Fairy Wing
-100% chance for Split Evil Ideas (BTL5)
-1250 ULT weapons will be additionally dropped from Deep Dark and Abyss difficulty
-1250 ULT weapons will be dropped as "Corrupted Force Weapon Selection Chest"

-Abyss difficulty has a higher rate than Deep Dark for that ^
-The Amount of EXP that you can gain from ES/Elite Supes is listed in this chart:




II:Â Â AddedÂ fancyÂ health bar to Elite Supes


-New health bar UI for each boss stage, with improved visibility
-Location of this health bar is upper center of your screen (and, ya can't move it, so get used to it)







III:Â  New Episode Quest


Requirements: 1125+ and you need to have done part 2 (Shining Binary Star)
Continue the questline at Bigaple Assoc. Branch Deputy Director



IV: New Sub Quest
Requirements: 1350+ and you need to have done "Cut the Stems" quest
Talk with Galerion Campsite NPC named Dispatch Member to start this quest
